547
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:18,396
Pi Pi, Ge Zheng, Dapeng, Jiang Yi!

548
00:33:18,396 --> 00:33:19,440
 Here! 

549
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:22,200
Go up and bring Captain Song back!

550
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:43,359
 - Captain! 
 - Captain! 

551
00:33:43,359 --> 00:33:45,159
 Junping! 

552
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:49,360
 Captain! 

553
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,859
Junping!

554
00:33:56,859 --> 00:33:59,359
- Captain! 
 - Captain!

555
00:33:59,359 --> 00:34:00,529
Junping!

556
00:34:00,529 --> 00:34:02,570
Junping!

557
00:34:02,570 --> 00:34:03,920
- Captain! 
 - Captain!

558
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:05,920
Captain!

