625
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,600
Say something.

626
00:38:55,119 --> 00:38:57,280
I guess we share...

627
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,380
some similar thoughts.

628
00:39:04,719 --> 00:39:07,211
I'll take that as a compliment.

